Malice nodded and transformed into his beast mode.  He wanders outside of the base, searching for lava tubes or something.  After about a megacycle of wandering and searching, he finally found a basalt based lava flow and transformed.  He wadded about knee deep and absorbed the heat so he would not melt or warp his legs.  He got a hand full of the heavy thick stuff, and drew the heat out, leaving a solid mass.  He then dipped it into the lava, pulled it out, and repeated the process until it was halfway up his chest after several megacycles.  He rolled it out of the lava stream and began to roll it back to the base.


Two megacycles later, Malice finally rolled the crude sphere like ball into the base.  He rolled it into the cargo bay, and went to find Wolfblade.
&quot;Hey Wolfblade, I finished the sphere!  Where are you?&quot;  

